{"tid":1587861,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"行動討論-和你shop可以全面取代遊行","createTime":"2019-09-22T14:52:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T16:01:21.000Z","uid":38991,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"07c7d63e44bfb4263af2c1a341f065390a7c94f6","tid":1587861,"uid":38991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T14:52:52.000Z","msg":"認真諗下，有咩係遊行做到而和你shop做唔到？<br />\n<br />\n遊行既目的:<br />\n1. 表達訴求:<br />\n有特別訴求既遊行可以繼續:去英領，美領勾結外國勢力，做比外媒睇，其他商場內都做到<br />\n<br />\n2.聚人數玩下場:<br />\n反對通知書+黨鐵預先封站，出到黎既人已經大減<br />\n<br />\n和你shop優點:<br />\n1.合法聚人數而唔需要申請，和理非容易參與<br />\n<br />\n2.商場位置一定交通方便容易走<br />\n<br />\n3.有效針對藍色商場同鋪頭，直接損害敵人利益<br />\n<br />\n4.黑警黨鐵商場反制措施有限<br />\n黑警:window shopping無犯法無藉口入場，商場不能用tg，最多派人附近戒備<br />\n黨鐵: 封站咪即係助攻影響商場生意，而且商場交通方便大量巴士去到<br />\n商場:禁制令？安檢？趕客？不如直接拉閘啦<br />\n<br />\n雖然今日效果理想，但係唔完美，可以改善，一齊討論下:<br />\n<br />\n1.商場內完全和理非，唔建議破壞設施同獅鳥<br />\n<br />\n同塞機場1.0同一道理，和理非已經達到目的，點解要用武力？有犯法事件就會引狗入場，引狗最大既問題係會影響到下一步，睇返今日4點左右已經令到商場可以拉閘，我地仲有大把時間玩下半場，有狗到就無咁方便<br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bb45e29b532492bfe8966c755fef14b0aa5215f","tid":1587861,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T14:52:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"ddb0246cb6b19cc55b78aa94cb0bf29d5a1523aa","tid":1587861,"uid":38991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T14:55:05.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"d5950722450afad4d22c27bc28bcdf615a9020e3","tid":1587861,"uid":38991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T14:56:54.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"3a439bdb35494a7548249a48674461cdc4a3654c","tid":1587861,"uid":7168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T14:58:39.000Z","msg":"禁下飛仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 叫下口號都落閘啦 <br />\n唔落閘都做唔到生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53fa42c73acb37e97c99799ed608e6d585803c6f","tid":1587861,"uid":158889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T14:58:56.000Z","msg":"可以討論"},{"pid":"690fe677fa6c716c884db6a7b3f05d6d1c512b5b","tid":1587861,"uid":274141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T15:01:06.000Z","msg":"10.1 IT/文宣事#<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587733\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587733</a>"},{"pid":"403924756127aef9e48bb9f199d9d2e51cf873e7","tid":1587861,"uid":38991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T15:03:48.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"ebe4dcecc5fb9fdc390bf6fad196c681770079f1","tid":1587861,"uid":38991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T15:04:19.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"1a657f6d8746240be6ebec8d7ee5c2b38f19b3e4","tid":1587861,"uid":38991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T15:06:06.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"fc5e347780fbd550f3d76d0b5b7a5fa238dc5e30","tid":1587861,"uid":52152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T15:10:22.000Z","msg":"長遠可以，但係重大日子(101)果啲都係要一齊行街集下氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"478ab9159db54eb802361ec861ef779c3c51c7dc","tid":1587861,"uid":38991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc5e347780fbd550f3d76d0b5b7a5fa238dc5e30","tid":1587861,"uid":52152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T15:10:22.000Z","msg":"長遠可以，但係重大日子(101)果啲都係要一齊行街集下氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T15:11:39.000Z","msg":"大遊行民陣個類可以繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cca1efc7de30950f01c089c79191133b7af983c5","tid":1587861,"uid":138609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T15:13:42.000Z","msg":"首先要頂到區議會選舉先<br />\n呢次港共一家會出術干預選舉<br />\n一係就DQ 一係選舉舞弊<br />\n因為港共唔靠出橫手大部分區都輸硬<br />\n到時係另一個升級時機<br />\n當然有可能放俾你贏<br />\n但諗深一層可能性極低"},{"pid":"c4affc9eaf2f13bffa8373d8d3096735fe75bddf","tid":1587861,"uid":38991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T15:30:51.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"db94d8ca1062e72f2759c2bbc092fd328cc5f493","tid":1587861,"uid":38991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:01:21.000Z","msg":"7/10"}]}